				<title>老李和老张的故事</title>
				<link>http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/old-friends-story</link>
				<description>

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: right;&quot;&gt;
&lt;table class=&quot;rate_t2 bhl-{$bhl}&quot;&gt;
